21:24.250 --> 21:26.503
BILL: I thought you looked familiar.

21:26.878 --> 21:28.171
Sofia.

21:28.254 --> 21:30.965
- It's Sophie.
- Well, Sofia is the Greek.

21:31.174 --> 21:33.802
Well, I'm named after a Sofia.

21:33.885 --> 21:38.223
I used to have a great-aunt
living on the mainland named Sofia.

21:38.973 --> 21:42.268
