I gotta go fix it.

22:16.344 --> 22:18.430
- Hey, listen, Donna? Donna.
- I'm serious. Move.

22:19.514 --> 22:20.598
Sit down!

22:20.682 --> 22:22.058
- She won't let me go!
- I know...

22:22.142 --> 22:24.769
I know you're going to make
a fortune with web's...

22:24.853 --> 22:27.397
- "With web's..."
- With Sky's site.

22:27.480 --> 22:29.023
I know you're gonna make a fortune with

22:29.107 --> 22:31.443
- Sky's website, but...
- It's good.

22:31.526 --> 22:33.403
Are you gonna be okay until then?

22:33.486 --> 22:35.947
I think Tanya is offering to pawn her bling.

22:36.030 --> 22:38.450
- No, seriously, Donna...
- Oh, my God.

22:38.533 --> 22:40.785
- Do you need a loan?
- No, sweet.

22:40.869 --> 22:44.497
Oh, God, I'm just whining, you know me.

22:44.581 --> 22:46.833
I don't need to be taken care of.

22:46.916 --> 22:49.544
Yeah, but are you being taken care of?

22:49.627 --> 22:52.297
- What do you mean?
- Are you getting any?

22:52.756 --> 22:53.798
Oh, you mean...

22:53.882 --> 22:57.469
(DRILL WHIRRING)

22:59.012 --> 23:02.098
Down, boy, down, boy.
No, it takes too much energy.

23:02.182 --> 23:05.226
Yeah. Just more plumbing
to be maintained, isn't it?

23:05.310 --> 23:06.603
Yeah.

23:06.686 --> 23:10.607
Oh, God, I'm so glad
that whole part of my life is over.

23:10.690 --> 23:12.275
You know, seriously.

23:12.358 --> 23:13.401
(EXHALES)

23:13.485 --> 23:15.820
I do not miss it at all.

23:17.072 --> 23:18.281
(CLEARS THROAT)

23:19.074 --> 23:20.200
(GOAT BLEATING)

23:20.283 --> 23:22.994
Then it's just right here. Good.

23:25.622 --> 23:27.791
Where's Donna? Hey! Okay.

23:29.959 --> 23:31.336
Up you go.

23:32.921 --> 23:34.297
(CHUCKLES)

23:37.300 --> 23:38.343
(GROANS SOFTLY)

23:40.011 --> 23:41.054
Hmm.

23:42.180 --> 23:44.057
You know,

23:44.140 --> 23:47.352
I don't want to seem ungrateful
for the scenic tour,

23:47.435 --> 23:48.978
but might I be shown my room now?

23:49.062 --> 23:52.399
Well, don't hold your breath, Harry,
but I think this is your room.

23:52.482 --> 23:53.983
Can we see Donna now?

23:55.193 --> 23:56.945
I sent the invites.

23:57.487 --> 23:59.489
My mom doesn't know anything.

23:59.572 --> 24:00.698
(SIGHING)

24:00.782 --> 24:01.825
